'''Reiðhöllin''' is an [[indoor arena]] located in [[Reykjavík]], [[Iceland]], which is used primarily as an [[Equestrianism|equestrian]] center. The hall is just over 1,800 m<sup>2</sup> in size; 26 meters wide and 70 meters long.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.svadastadir.is/page/adstada |title=Aðstaða &#124; Reiðhöllin Svaðastaðir |publisher=Svadastadir.is |date= |accessdate=2014-06-01}}</ref> It has also hosted concerts, including performances by [[Kiss (band)|Kiss]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.setlist.fm/setlist/kiss/1988/reihollin-reykjavik-iceland-43dcfbb3.html |title=KISS Concert Setlist at Reiðhöllin, Reykjavik on August 30, 1988 |publisher=setlist.fm |date= |accessdate=2014-06-01}}</ref> in 1988 and [[Whitesnake]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.setlist.fm/setlist/whitesnake/1990/reihollin-reykjavik-iceland-63dbeac7.html |title=Whitesnake Concert Setlist at Reiðhöllin, Reykjavik on September 7, 1990 |publisher=setlist.fm |date= |accessdate=2014-06-01}}</ref> in 1990.

